### Listar tareas
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks

### Crear tarea valida
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Estudiar FastAPI",
  "priority": 3,
  "done": false
}

### Crear tarea invalida (title corto)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hi",
  "priority": 3,
  "done": false
}

### Buscar tarea inexistente
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks/999
